                            <h3>ITIL Workshop Experience</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-4">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-1">1. What are the modes of training offered for the&nbsp;ITIL 4 Foundation Certification Course?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The ITIL4 Foundation workshop at KnowledgeHut is delivered through PRISM, our immersive learning experience platform, via two modes of delivery:</p>
                                            <p><b>Blended learning:</b></p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>With live and interactive instructor-led training events and the convenience and flexibility of self-paced study, you can have the best of both worlds.</li>
                                                <li>Listen, study, ask questions, and have your instructor, who is an experienced practitioner, clear up any doubts you may have.<br></li>
