                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-3-15">15. Where to purchase my ITIL Exam Voucher?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-3-15" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The examination voucher can only be bought directly from Peoplecert’s website or through an accredited course provider.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-3-16">16. How to get the ITIL® voucher from Pearson VUE to schedule the ITIL® Exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-3-16" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Follow the below steps to get the&nbsp; ITIL® voucher from Pearson VUE to schedule the&nbsp; ITIL exam:</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><b>Step 1: </b>Log onto <a href="https://wsr.pearsonvue.com/vouchers/pricelist/peoplecert.asp" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Pearson Vue.</a></li>
                                                <li><b>Step 2: </b>Select your country and check the voucher prices for different certifications.</li>
                                                <li><b>Step 3:</b> Download the voucher form corresponding to your region and fill the form.</li>
                                                <li><b>Step 4:</b> Submit the form. If you encounter any error submitting the form online, you can also email/fax them the form.</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-3-17">17. What is the validity of my voucher once I receive it from Peoplecert?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-3-17" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p><b>Duration -</b>Once you obtain the voucher, it is valid for 12 months or 1 year since the effective day. For ITIL® Examination, the voucher is available in two different languages&nbsp; -<br></p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>&nbsp;ITIL Foundation (English)&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>&nbsp;ITIL Foundation (JPN)</li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p><b>Conditions -&nbsp;</b>These vouchers are not customizable. It means that the voucher has to be used according to the examination guidelines.<br></p>
                                            <p><b>Pricing -&nbsp;</b>The voucher price includes additional charges with the addition of VAT.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-3-18">18. Is the ITIL Foundation an open-book or closed-book exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-3-18" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>This is a closed book exam, and electronic devices are not allowed.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
