                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-4-27">27. How many credits can you earn at the end of ITIL® V3 Intermediate Service Design module?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-4-27" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-4">
