                                                            </ul>
                                                            <p>The second option is to become an <b>ITIL Strategic Leader (ITIL SL)</b> after the ITIL V4 foundation exam candidates have to finish two modules and must have at least 3 years of managerial experience to become an ITIL SL. The modules are:</p>
                                                            <ul>
