                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-10-3">3. What does a service manager do?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-10-3" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-10">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>A service manager states the services to be rendered and also makes sure that the services rendered meet the company’s needs and are rendered in accordance with the requirement of the business. The service manager identifies the service team and also sets up activities and meetings.He or she will lead the team through the service life-cycle and also ensure adequate communication between client representatives, service delivery and support personnel, and ITS management. The service manager will work with the service team to ensure external service providers are managed properly, and tasks are assigned to technicians based on skills and availability.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
