                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="my-itil-badge">
                            <h3>My ITIL® Badge</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="seo-content-accordion-11">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-1">1. What is My AXELOS?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>My AXELOS is designed to provide professionals with the best practices and most updated publications. It is an online subscription which allows the learners to enhance their understanding and skills by giving them access to the best methods provided by ITIL®. In order to help the students grasp the concepts better, the online content subscription provides all the resources and tools, everything one needs to boost their careers. Ultimately, My AXELOS is a place where you will find everything from the best practices, newest updates, and your earned digital badges.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-2">2. How much does the AXELOS membership cost?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-2" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The annual membership cost of the AXELOS is&nbsp; <b>£59</b>.(<a href="https://www.peoplecert.org/browse-certifications/it-governance-and-service-management/ITIL-1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Link</a>.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-3">3. What are the benefits of subscribing to My AXELOS?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-3" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The major benefits of subscribing to My AXELOS are as follows:</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><b>Reliable resources</b>My AXELOS offers the most reliable resources. They provide everything from publications, methods to tools which are needed for a career boost. The best part is, one can get access to all these in just a few clicks.<br></li>
                                                <li><b>Regular Updates</b>The subscription gives regular updates on what's happening inside the industry.<br></li>
                                                <li><b>Expert guidance </b>They provide highly qualified experts. This gives the students an opportunity to train with the best in the industry.<br></li>
                                                <li><b>Validation</b>The digital badge is proof of the candidate’s skills and expertise in the field. Moreover, ITIL® requires continuous enhancement of knowledge because of which the student has to complete the continuing professional development or CPD activities every year to retain the badge.</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-4">4. What is My ITIL?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-4" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>My ITIL® is designed to assist the student effectively utilize the expertise achieved from the ITIL Foundation and implement it in their professional life. It is an online content subscription which will help to get constant updates, therefore making it easy to adopt new skills and knowledge which will be as per the future innovations in the sector.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-5">5. Is My ITIL® a paid subscription or is it free?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-5" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>My ITIL® is a <b>1-year subscription</b>. It is free for professionals applying for the ITIL® Intermediate exam.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-6">6. What is the purpose of subscribing to My ITIL?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-6" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The major purpose of My ITIL® is as follows:</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Complete access to the best practices offered by ITIL. It also allows the student to obtain the latest publications which assist the student throughout their ITIL® course.<br></li>
                                                <li>Advanced toolkit to enhance understanding.<br></li>
                                                <li>Exclusive whitepapers.<br></li>
                                                <li>A digital badge and certification to showcase the gained knowledge and expertise.</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-7">7. What is ITIL® Digital Badge?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-7" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>ITIL® Digital Badge is awarded to the students who have cleared the ITIL® examination. It appears as icons and is an indication of the knowledge gained by the person.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-8">8. How do I earn an ITIL® Digital Badge?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-8" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>One can earn the ITIL® Digital Badge if they meet the CPD requirements. As soon as the requirements are met, the digital badge is issued. It's valid until the subscription expires.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-9">9. How do I renew my ITIL® Digital Badge?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-9" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>A candidate needs to gain a minimum of <b>20 CPD</b> to extend the validity of the badge for the next 12 months.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#seo-content-heading-11-10">10. What are the CPD requirements?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="seo-content-heading-11-10" class="collapse" data-parent="#seo-content-accordion-11">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>ITIL® keeps revising and updating their courses. Therefore, it also expects the students to be a part of this continuous learning process. Continuing Professional Development or CDP was designed with various activities which will enhance the skills in professional life. The whole requirement is divided into 3 stages to ease the process. The steps are as follows -<br></p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><b>Step1:&nbsp;</b>Evaluate the skills and abilities, this will help the candidates understand their development and give them a perspective of where they stand. Moreover, this will also allow them to determine the areas where they have to work. The evaluation also provides them with a list of various activities exclusively for them as per their needs.<br></li>
                                                <li><b>Step 2:&nbsp;</b>Once the student understands where they need to improve and what the development goals are, they can enroll in the development centers which will train them as per their choice of activities.<br></li>
                                                <li><b>Step 3:&nbsp;</b>Ultimately, the final stage concentrates on the result of the activities performed in order to achieve the goals. Here, the student’s understanding will be tested based on the outcome and they will be asked to describe their learning experience throughout the development period.</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
