            "name": "What are the key benefits of ITIL® V3 Intermediate IT Planning, Protection, and Optimisation certification?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The key benefits of ITIL® V3 Intermediate IT Planning, Protection, and Optimisation certification are as follows:<br></p><ol><li><b>Get more valuable skills&nbsp;</b>Get equipped with a highly-demanded certification.<br></li><li><b>Learn PPO best practice&nbsp;</b>Deliver services that meet business needs by equipping yourself with the knowledge of the best practices.<br></li><li><b>Understand the processes&nbsp;</b>Get a valuable understanding of the ITIL® Service Design processes.</li></ol>"
            }
