                "text": "<p>You can claim for your ITIL® Practitioner badge by becoming a My AXELOS subscriber.</p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What should I do to maintain the ITIL® Practitioner digital badge?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
