                "text": "<div>Salary of a Project Manager having an&nbsp; ITIL® V3 certification or&nbsp; ITIL V4 certification varies from country to country. We have covered them below:<br><br></div><div></div><ul><li><b>India:</b> The national average salary for a Project Manager is INR 1,251,978 in India.<br></li><li><b>US:</b> The national average salary for a Project Manager is $132,453 in United States.<br></li><li><b>UK:</b> The national average salary for a Project Manager is £61,188 in United Kingdom.</li></ul>"
            }
        }, {
